# Third-party assets bundled in this repository

The following data and model assets are redistributed under their own licenses:

- `data/finding_labels_rate.csv` and `data/reports_25k.csv` are derived from the
  Merlin Abdominal CT dataset (Stanford). Refer to the source dataset's terms
  before re-redistributing beyond research use.
- `checkpoints/concat_rate_probe.pt` is a linear probe trained over Merlin +
  Pillar-0 features on the above dataset. Distributed under MIT alongside the
  code; respect the source dataset's research-use terms.

The following weights are NOT bundled but referenced for download:

- Merlin encoder (`stanfordmimi/Merlin`, MIT)
  https://huggingface.co/stanfordmimi/Merlin
- Pillar-0 encoder (`YalaLab/Pillar0-AbdomenCT`, permissive license)
  https://huggingface.co/YalaLab/Pillar0-AbdomenCT
- Merlin imaging dataset (Stanford / Azure-hosted) — see README.md
